OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1776611465
OL,3,CMan who felled Sycamore Gap tree
OL,4,Creleased from prison
OL,6,FNorthumberland Correspondent Tom
OL,7,FBarton has been gauging reaction to
OL,8,Fthe release from prison of Adam
OL,9,FCarruthers who felled the famous
OL,10,FSycamore Gap tree
OL,12,FThe man who felled the Sycamore Gap
OL,13,Ftree has been released from prison
OL,14,Fafter serving just 10 months of a four
OL,15,Fyear and three month sentence, ITV
OL,16,FNews Tyne Tees can exclusively reveal.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
