FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1776611465
OL,3,CMan who felled Sycamore Gap tree
OL,4,Creleased from prison
OL,6,FAdam Carruthers, 33, was jailed in May
OL,7,F2025 after being convicted alongside
OL,8,Fhis former friend Daniel Graham, 40,
OL,9,Fof felling the much-loved
OL,10,FNorthumberland tree and damage to
OL,11,FHadrian's Wall in September 2023.
OL,13,FHowever, ITV News Tyne Tees
OL,14,Funderstands that Carruthers, who gave
OL,15,Fhis address in court as Wigton,
OL,16,FCumbria, was released in March under
OL,17,Fcurfew and is required to wear an
OL,18,Felectronic tag.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1776611465
OL,3,CMan who felled Sycamore Gap tree
OL,4,Creleased from prison
OL,6,FWhen we visited Cumbria Turf in
OL,7,FKirkbride, the business identified
OL,8,Fduring his trial as Carruthers'
OL,9,Femployer, we found him in a workshop
OL,10,Fsurrounded by old vehicles.
OL,12,FAked if he was happy to be out of
OL,13,Fjail, he told us he was. Asked whether
OL,14,Fhe was back at work, he nodded.
OL,16,FSteve Blair, general manager from
OL,17,FTwice Brewed Inn, near Sycamore Gap,
OL,18,Fsaid he was "shocked" to learn of
OL,19,FCarruthers' return home.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1776611465
OL,3,CMan who felled Sycamore Gap tree
OL,4,Creleased from prison
OL,6,FThe pub, which welcomes many walkers
OL,7,Falong Hadrian's Wall, is home to a
OL,8,Fslice of the felled tree.
OL,10,FThe decision to release Carruthers
OL,11,Fwas, ITV News understands, taken by
OL,12,Fthe governor at the prison where he
OL,13,Fwas serving his sentence after a risk
OL,14,Fassessment was carried out.
OL,16,FHe has been released under the
OL,17,Fgovernment's Home Detention Curfew
OL,18,FScheme, which allows prisoners to
OL,19,Fserve part of their sentence at home.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1776611465
OL,3,CMan who felled Sycamore Gap tree
OL,4,Creleased from prison
OL,6,FThey are expected to wear an
OL,7,Felectronic tag, and to spend between
OL,8,Fnine and around 12 hours a day at
OL,9,Ftheir registered home address.
OL,11,FBoth Carruthers and Graham, from near
OL,12,FCarlisle, were sentenced to four years
OL,13,Fand three months imprisonment.
OL,15,FThey were told by the judge, Mrs
OL,16,FJustice Lambert, they would serve a
OL,17,Fmaximum of 40 percent of the sentence.
OL,18,FThat would have meant Carruthers would
OL,19,Fhave been released in January 2027.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1776611465
OL,3,CMan who felled Sycamore Gap tree
OL,4,Creleased from prison
OL,6,FBut under the Home Detention Curfew
OL,7,FScheme, prisoners can be released
OL,8,Fafter serving half of that time, a
OL,9,Fdate which, for Carruthers, would have
OL,10,Fbeen around 15 March this year.
OL,12,FA Ministry of Justice spokesperson
OL,13,Ftold ITV News: "Anyone released into
OL,14,FHome Detention Curfew faces strict
OL,15,Flicence conditions and must be tagged.
OL,16,FThose who break the rules can be
OL,17,Freturned to prison."
OL,19,FSome of the walkers at Sycamore Gap on
OL,20,FWednesday (15 April) were not
OL,21,Fimpressed with Carruthers' release.
OL,26,@uD@POUyD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1776611465
OL,3,CMan who felled Sycamore Gap tree
OL,4,Creleased from prison
OL,6,FOne woman said it was "unbelievable"
OL,7,Fand "he shouldn't be at liberty",
OL,8,Fadding: "I'm not every impressed about
OL,9,Fthat at all. For what he's done - what
OL,10,Fhe's done for this area and wjhat he's
OL,11,Fdone to our culture, no, he shouldn't
OL,12,Fbe allowed to do that."
OL,14,FAnother man said: "How important that
OL,15,Fis - it might be a little soon in the
OL,16,Fmeasurement of punishment."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1776611465
OL,3,CMan who felled Sycamore Gap tree
OL,4,Creleased from prison
OL,6,FHelen Lloyd, from Dartmoor, had a
OL,7,Fdifferent view. She said: "If he's
OL,8,Flearned and I think a lot of other
OL,9,Fpeople have learned because of the
OL,10,Fpublicity so I think it's alright - I
OL,11,Fthink he's probably had his due."
OL,13,FAfter his conviction, Carruthers
OL,14,Fadmitted to probation officers that he
OL,15,Fhad wielded the chainsaw and felled
OL,16,Fthe tree while his friend Daniel
OL,17,FGraham filmed him doing so.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1776611465
OL,3,CMan who felled Sycamore Gap tree
OL,4,Creleased from prison
OL,6,FDuring the trial at Newcastle Crown
OL,7,FCourt in April 2025, jurors heard how
OL,8,FGraham, of Millbeck Stables, Carlisle,
OL,9,Fand Carruthers, of Church Street,
OL,10,FWigton, drove for 40 miles from the
OL,11,FCarlisle area to the Sycamore Gap site
OL,12,Fon 28 September 2023.
OL,14,FThe court was shown a video, found on
OL,15,FGraham's phone, which captured the
OL,16,Fmoment the tree was chopped down in
OL,17,Fthe pitch black, before it fell
OL,18,Fbackwards onto Hadrian's Wall.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1776611465
OL,3,CMan who felled Sycamore Gap tree
OL,4,Creleased from prison
OL,6,FIt caused #622,191 of criminal damage
OL,7,Fto the tree as well as causing #1,144
OL,8,Fof damage to Hadrian's Wall, a Unesco
OL,9,FWorld Heritage Site. Both are owned by
OL,10,Fthe National Trust.
OL,12,FThe prosecution also claimed the men
OL,13,Ftook a wedge from the tree as a
OL,14,Ftrophy. It, and the chainsaw believed
OL,15,Fto have been used to cut the tree
OL,16,Fdown, were never found.
OL,18,FSentencing the pair in July last year,
OL,19,FJudge Lambert dismissed said she
OL,20,Fbelieved they were "both equally
OL,21,Fculpable" for felling the tree.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
